      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>DonateKind was created with a simple goal – to make giving easier and more accessible. We believe that donations aren't just about money. Items like clothes, books, toys, and food can bring joy and help to others in need.</p>

      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>We are a group of students passionate about social good and technology. DonateKind is our way of combining both to create impact.</p>
