  </header>
  <main>
    <section>
      <h2>Step 1: Fill Out the Form</h2>
      <p>Go to the homepage and fill in your name, the item you want to donate, and the pickup location.</p>

      <h2>Step 2: We Connect</h2>
      <p>Our team or volunteers will get in touch with you to confirm pickup or drop-off details.</p>

      <h2>Step 3: Donation Delivered</h2>
      <p>Your donation will be delivered to an organization or person in need. You make a difference!</p>
    </section>
